@CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5019

### Leads - Get All
GET {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/leads
Accept: application/json

### Leads - Get By Id
GET {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/leads/{{leadId}}
Accept: application/json

### Leads - Create
POST {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "555-0100",
  "source": "Website",
  "status": "New"
}

### Leads - Update
PUT {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/leads/{{leadId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "555-0200",
  "source": "Referral",
  "status": "Contacted"
}

### Leads - Delete
DELETE {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/leads/{{leadId}}

### Deals - Get All
GET {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/deals
Accept: application/json

### Deals - Get By Id
GET {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/deals/{{dealId}}
Accept: application/json

### Deals - Create
POST {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/deals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Enterprise License",
  "value": 50000.00,
  "closeDate": "2026-03-15",
  "stage": "Prospecting",
  "leadId": "{{leadId}}"
}

### Deals - Update
PUT {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/deals/{{dealId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Enterprise License - Renewed",
  "value": 75000.00,
  "closeDate": "2026-06-01",
  "stage": "Negotiation",
  "leadId": "{{leadId}}"
}

### Deals - Delete
DELETE {{CrmDotnetApi_HostAddress}}/api/deals/{{dealId}}
